channel.title: Looking for people who want to make a good server!
channel.description:
Hello everyone,
Im want to make a new server with many features and nice people. So im looking for 1 or 2 people who want and can help me with developing a server and keep running it. If you want to help you must have experience with coding in java. I'll arrange the hosting for the server and of course i help with developing the server.
Greetings,
Yohurt / Bas
